objectProperties.label: personal mailbox
objectProperties.comment: A  personal mailbox, ie. an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the first owner of this mailbox. This is a 'static inverse functional property', in that  there is (across time and change) at most one individual that ever has any particular value for foaf:mbox.

objectProperties.label: based near
objectProperties.comment: A location that something is based near, for some broadly human notion of near.

objectProperties.label: phone
objectProperties.comment: A phone,  specified using fully qualified tel: URI scheme (refs: http://www.w3.org/Addressing/schemes.html#tel).
